turns.assistant:
In your V2Ray config (`config.json`), set the outbound to use IPv4 only:

**Option 1: Force IPv4 in freedom outbound**

```json
{
  "outbounds": [
    {
      "protocol": "freedom",
      "settings": {
        "domainStrategy": "UseIPv4"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

